/**
 * Feature-based modules (vertical slices).
 *
 * Each module is self-contained:
 *   features/<module-name>/
 *     components/    Module-specific UI
 *     hooks/         Module-specific hooks
 *     services/      Module API services
 *     types/         Module types
 *     utils/         Module utilities
 *     index.ts       Public API barrel export
 *
 * Planned modules:
 * - website          Hotel public website
 * - booking          Direct booking engine
 * - pms              Property management
 * - front-desk       Reception operations
 * - housekeeping     Room status & tasks
 * - restaurant       POS & menu
 * - room-service     QR ordering
 * - corporate        B2B portal
 * - inventory        Stock management
 * - purchase         Procurement
 * - vendors          Vendor management
 * - maintenance      Work orders
 * - hrms             Human resources
 * - finance          Accounting & billing
 * - crm              Guest relationship
 * - reports          Analytics & exports
 * - owner-dashboard  Owner KPIs
 * - investor         Investor reporting
 * - ai-analytics     AI insights
 * - integrations     Third-party connectors
 * - admin            Super admin panel
 */
